dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T21:06:04.000Z","msg":"我個人經驗係先分開左右手<br />\n右手係主旋律 正常拍子速度高低音都會熟啲<br />\n可以淨係試下右手先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n左手通常係伴奏<br />\n建議你練熟右手先<br />\n跟住再慢慢逐個bar加埋左手試<br />\n同埋練既時候最好由頭開始<br />\n即係練熟小節1先<br />\n跟住1&gt;2<br />\n跟住1&gt;2&gt;3 如此類推 推到成隻歌<br />\n咁樣肌肉記憶會好啲 好快掌握到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n初級既歌好多都係千篇一律既<br />\n特別係流行曲果種<br />\n最緊要有心練同唔怕悶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T21:11:15.000Z","msg":"多謝你嘅分享 我會努力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01cc7fdf994f731d06c4a594f99ceca8b1cd61f5","tid":807771,"uid":88887,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T23:28:00.000Z","msg":"學琴有咩用"},{"pid":"7047ffd07cef07565644391d062314533f371c9c","tid":807771,"uid":127176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3cbc81f8cb3a452664636cee2506d1a01edb7faa","tid":807771,"uid":65774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dcb39fcaaed1622b01acb46368a7581e9ef62f0","tid":807771,"uid":127176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f432c3e748fcc5fb920de148730c5a8c09ec6aa","tid":807771,"uid":65774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T20:03:26.000Z","msg":"分手各自練熟然後慢慢夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以試下對拍子機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T20:14:27.000Z","msg":"樓主嘅問題係兩隻手夾唔到唔同速度<br />\n再對拍子機只會令佢分心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T20:19:08.000Z","msg":"係咁架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為夾拍子機可以令佢知道左手右手分別係一拍之內要做幾多野，會改善到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T03:42:53.000Z","msg":"拍子機嘅作用係幫人以固定節拍彈奏<br />\n因為唔係個個都有好強嘅節奏感，冇拍子機嘅話有時彈快或者彈慢咗都唔自知<br />\n<br />\n但前提係要彈得順首歌先<br />\n係未做到呢樣嘢之前應該以自己適應到嘅速度嚟彈<br />\n開拍子機迫自己跟足一個節拍反而會加添咗壓力<br />\n我以前學琴果陣有時未練熟就跟拍子機會搞到亂咗<br />\n<br />\n或者可以試下單手果陣對下拍子<br />\n但合手一開始要練熟少少協調到先好再對拍子"},{"pid":"586fa7721d3045ac8719b6fe3b99f82cffed3868","tid":807771,"uid":202869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01cc7fdf994f731d06c4a594f99ceca8b1cd61f5","tid":807771,"uid":88887,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T23:28:00.000Z","msg":"學琴有咩用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:00:15.000Z","msg":"人人興趣唔同 唔需要問有咩用"},{"pid":"3951fbfb3d10f2c6693053a37dbae0fd1a59b78c","tid":807771,"uid":116105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c123ae38443e396a26eaf1c9c449bb88aac17fc","tid":807771,"uid":38558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T20:00:31.000Z","msg":"廢撚經驗係時間同練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 初頭慢慢彈幾次，熟習之後按返拍子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:03:45.000Z","msg":"thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecaee0f83aa824d6adea367db122dfcff9c5c1b9","tid":807771,"uid":174972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"留名 學左3個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3d9d35550a4e0c3b77531928bd346114b0dfe9","tid":807771,"uid":196682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:12:25.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n7級左好耐,考唔上第8級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069deec868603eb1b367b08a6f6c6449f158b9e4","tid":807771,"uid":202869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecaee0f83aa824d6adea367db122dfcff9c5c1b9","tid":807771,"uid":174972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"留名 學左3個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"一齊加油 我上左3個月堂 琴就買左2個月 當學左2個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83f84dbbe4c76e03a2af2e60db5b2224a912d99","tid":807771,"uid":202869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd3d9d35550a4e0c3b77531928bd346114b0dfe9","tid":807771,"uid":196682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:12:25.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n7級左好耐,考唔上第8級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:33:41.000Z","msg":"對於我黎講 太遙遠<br />\n唔好灰心呀 考到係遲早既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76438d00ee38b9508cff3d690db95aa67f5d3ce2","tid":807771,"uid":196682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c83f84dbbe4c76e03a2af2e60db5b2224a912d99","tid":807771,"uid":202869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd3d9d35550a4e0c3b77531928bd346114b0dfe9","tid":807771,"uid":196682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:12:25.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n7級左好耐,考唔上第8級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:33:41.000Z","msg":"對於我黎講 太遙遠<br />\n唔好灰心呀 考到係遲早既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:40:51.000Z","msg":"其實我都有協調問題,問過MISS好多次<br />\nMISS都係答我要自己搵岩自己既方法 同埋練多D琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我都覺得講左等於冇講,答左等於冇答咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係熟能生巧又真係岩既!自己睇番自己1級同而家7級都已經好唔同啦<br />\n所以樓主要繼續比心機練琴!每練一次都會比上一次熟左DD<br />\n練下練下就會成功嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a030d6d6111e5844743b67e1178559f0b038e0","tid":807771,"uid":78099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:44:43.000Z","msg":"瘋狂練scale 每日練返半個鐘一個鐘"},{"pid":"6d1e56b567112151aab939a4ed202659321fb484","tid":807771,"uid":174972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"069deec868603eb1b367b08a6f6c6449f158b9e4","tid":807771,"uid":202869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"